## âš™ï¸ Database Setup

1. Start **MySQL** using XAMPP
2. Open **[localhost/phpMyAdmin](http://localhost/phpmyadmin/)**
3. Create database:
   ```sql
   CREATE DATABASE student_db;

## Select student_db and create table:

CREATE TABLE students (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100),
    department VARCHAR(50),
    roll INT UNIQUE
);

## Database Configuration

Update credentials in DBConnection.java if required:

DriverManager.getConnection(
    "jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/student_db",
    "root",
    "YOUR_PASSWORD"        //agar tera php my admin open huaa to pasword mat rakh)
);

## How to Run the Projec --->tere terminal mai past kar one by one
Step 1: Open Project Folder main.java

cd StudentManagementSystem

Step 2: Compile the Code

javac -cp .;mysql-connector-j-9.6.0.jar *.java

Step 3: Run the Program

java -cp .;mysql-connector-j-9.6.0.jar Main




